This project leverages Pivot Tables and Pivot Charts to transform raw retail sales data into interactive business reports. Sales trends are analyzed across products, regions, categories, and time periods to identify growth patterns and business opportunities. The project demonstrates how Pivot Tables simplify large datasets into meaningful summaries for faster decision-making.

Key Skills Demonstrated:
Pivot Tables
Pivot Charts
Trend Analysis
Sales Analytics
Business Reporting
Data Summarization
Interactive Excel Reports
Retail Insights
